<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178260>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Keilbachia oligonema sp. n. (A, B holotype, C, D, E the other specimen). A, part of hypopygium, ventral view. B, gonostylus, ventral view. C, basomedial part of hypopygium, ventral view. D, E, mesial megasetae of gonostylus, ventral view. Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178260/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178252>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Maxillary palpus. A, Keilbachia acamptochaeta sp. n. (paratype). B, K. flabellata sp. n. (holotype). C, K. gigas sp. n. (holotype). D, K. fasciata sp. n. (holotype). E, K. foveolata sp. n. (holotype). F, K. bicuspis sp. n. (holotype). G, K. rima sp. n. (holotype). H, K. filigera sp. n. (holotype). I, K. oligonema sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178252/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178256>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Eye bridge, frontal view (A), and part of hypopygium (B, D) and gonostylus (C, E), ventral view. A, B, C, Keilbachia acamptochaeta sp. n. (holotype). D, E, K. bicuspis sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178256/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178261>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Keilbachia rima sp. n. (A, C, holotype, B, D, E paratypes). A, B, eye bridge, frontal view. C, part of hypopygium, ventral view. D, gonostylus, ventral view. E, mesial side of gonostylus, ventral view. F, medial part of hypopygium, ventral view. Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178261/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178257>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Part of hypopygium (A, C) and gonostylus (B, D), ventral view. A, B, Keilbachia filigera sp. n. (holotype). C, D, K. fasciata sp. n. (holotype). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178257/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178259>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Eye bridge (A, B), frontal view, part of hypopygium (C, E) and gonostylus (D, F), ventral view. A, E, F, Keilbachia gigas sp. n. (holotype). B, C, D, K. foveolata sp. n. (B, D, E holotype, C non-type). Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178259/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.178258>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Keilbachia flabellata sp. n. (A, B, and C paratypes, D holotype). A, C, part of hypopygium, ventral view. B, D, gonostylus, ventral view. Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178258/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

